$ Csound: instrument
@ instrument

An instrument defines an algorithm.

{ Initiating an instrument

  The instrument's algorithm executes when the instrument is *initiated*.

  The initiation is triggered by an → Kunst/Musik/Csound/event.

  The initiation of the instrument places it onto the → Kunst/Musik/Csound/processing-chain.

  TODO: → Kunst/Musik/Csound/init-pass

}

{ Instrument 0 #instrument-0

  A special instrument 0 is uzed to → Kunst/Musik/Csound/init-pass#initialize-global-vars[initialize global variables etc.].

}

